<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-693] Sample 153 is Broken</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-693</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sample 153 doesn&apos;t work as expected. Synapse is supposed to get the secured message and route it to the backend service as it is. But it removes the security headers during the process. Hence the request fails at the backend server.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
